To build Mifos Business Intelligence source code including tests you need
 - Sun JDK 1.6.x
 - Maven 3.0.x
 - Gradle 0.9
 - Groovy 1.7.3+
 - Python 2.5+
 - MySQL 5.1.x
 - Pentaho Data Integration 4.1.0-stable
 - Download http://kettle4.s3.amazonaws.com/PentahoReporting.zip extract and drop pentaho-reporting-plugin.jar to
   data-integration-4.1.0-stable/plugins/pentaho-reporting-plugin.jar

Run bi/presto/install.py
 - give absolute location to Pentaho Data integration folder 
  example: /home/john/pdi-4.1.0-stable/data-integration
  
  Other things
  need to have a softlink for bi/reports/i18n/org under pentaho-di
   
